1. At line 1860: `xmlNodeListGetString((xmlDocPtr) sxe->document->ptr, node->children, 1);` - there's no check for `sxe->document` being NULL before dereferencing `sxe->document->ptr`.

2. At line 1871: `xmlNodeListGetString((xmlDocPtr) sxe->document->ptr, sxe->node->node->children, 1);` - same issue, no check for `sxe->document` being NULL.

